sub_title: Portuguese, English and German speaker based in the Netherlands. Open for jobs in the customer service or  sales where I can make use of my diverse set of languages, organizational skills and passion for customer care.
summary:
I am a Portuguese, English and German speaker currently based in the Netherlands. Following my passion for children, I have spent 2019 doing a language exchange with a German host family in Hamburg as a daycare mother, after which I finished a volunteer year in 2020 with in a bilingual Kindergarden in Hamburg.
As a problem solver with four years of work experience in the customer service and compliance sector with the PNB Paribas/Cetelem Bank in Sao Paulo, this is something I am looking to build on here. I am open for jobs in the customer service field where I can make use of my diverse set of language and organizational skills gathered over the past years, and work together with motivated colleagues.
